Package uk.ac.bris.cs.scotlandyard.model

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.bris.cs.scotlandyard.model.Player
  • public final class Player
extends Object
    A POJO representing an immutable player of the ScotlandYard game. Each player contains the Piece (coloured counter), ScotlandYard.Tickets, and the location.
